<style type="text/css">
.form-signin {
    max-width: 300px;
    padding: 19px 29px 29px;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
    background-color: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    -webkit-border-radius: 5px;
    -moz-border-radius: 5px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    -webkit-box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.05);
    -moz-box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.05);
    box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.05);
}
.form-signin .form-signin-heading,
.form-signin .checkbox {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.form-signin input[type="text"],
.form-signin input[type="password"] {
    font-size: 16px;
    height: auto;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    padding: 7px 9px;
}
</style>
<form class="form-signin" method="POST" action="/login">
  <h2 class="form-signin-heading">请登录</h2>
  <p>如果账号不存在，将会自动创建。所以，请牢记密码。</p>
  <% IF errmsg %><p class="alert alert-error"><% errmsg %></p><% END %>
  <input name="nick" maxlength="20" type="text" class="input-block-level" placeholder="昵称" value="<% nick %>">
  <input name="pass" maxlength="30" type="password" class="input-block-level" placeholder="密码">
  <label class="checkbox">
    <input type="checkbox" value="remember-me"> 记住我
  </label>
  <button class="btn btn-large btn-primary" type="submit">登录</button>
</form>
